title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 - Dec 21 2021

description:
Flashback: Rush Limbaugh, who Buck thanks for giving him his big break and leading the way, reads Buck's tweets from 2020. Our mission is to continue flying the conservative media mother ship that Rush expertly built. Psaki's latest covid prescription is deja vu all over again. Joining Buck: Blake Masters, president of the Thiel Foundation and COO of Thiel Capital, a Tucson native running for U.S. Senate in Arizona. Buck asks him about lawmakers owning stock, becoming rich from insider trading, the Biden economy, inflation and Democrat lies. Buck provides live commentary of Biden's shameful press conference where Biden, of course, falsely blames fhe unvaxxed for his failures.
